'''H-3PO''' was a name used by [[Popara Anjiliac Diresto|Popara]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt's]] group of [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droids]]. The [[Droid/Legends|droids]] relayed information updates between themselves on a regular basis, allowing them to coordinate chores and errands while still communicating with their fellow droids. For example, [[H-3POA]] was given to [[Vago Gejalli Thokka|Vago]] for use in negotiating. [[H-3POB]] served onboard the ''[[Imru Ootmian]]'', Popara's personal [[Starship/Legends|starship]]. H-3PO droids were different from other [[3PO-series protocol droid/Legends|3PO-series protocol droids]] because their access systems were able to understand a verbal signal from a specific individual. They had advanced sensors and communications systems, and were even designed with self-destruct mechanisms.

